---
title: Beef Spring Roll-Inspired Bowls with Crispy Shallots
description: We're transforming everyone's favourite appetizer into a delicious dinner! This deconstructed spring roll bowl is packed with soft, fluffy jasmine rice; crispy shallots; savoury, sticky beef and crunchy slaw. Top it all with a drizzle of plum sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-spring-roll-inspired-bowls-db66034d.jpg
